title: Flacco another Elway QB head-scratcher; Lamar Jackson unsustainable long-term; Antonio Brown and OBJ trade talk
itunes:title: Flacco another Elway QB head-scratcher; Lamar Jackson unsustainable long-term; Antonio Brown and OBJ trade talk
description:
In this episode, Middlekauff looks at John Elway trading for another "meh" QB in Joje Flacco, why doesn't think the Ravens building around Lamar Jackson is unsustainable, Antonio Brown and Odell Beckham trade rumors, and answers questions in Middlekauff Mailbag.
